{"type": "article", "id": 29309, "title": "优衣库在巴黎高定时装周发布首秀，以及，RAINS 秋冬款不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-07-08T03:01:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1124, "name": "巴黎"}, {"id": 3018, "name": "高级定制"}, {"id": 15794, "name": "秋冬"}, {"id": 29942, "name": "高定时装周"}, {"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}, {"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}, {"id": 1582, "name": "爱马仕"}, {"id": 2326, "name": "Gap"}, {"id": 3350, "name": "Louis Vuitton"}, {"id": 6459, "name": "雅芳"}, {"id": 13154, "name": "露华浓"}, {"id": 19682, "name": "Rains"}, {"id": 29943, "name": "Uniqlo U"}, {"id": 7576, "name": "Christophe Lemaire"}, {"id": 29944, "name": "Xavier Dolan"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160708103058OSKn08DxXA6vEa2q.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Caroline-de-Maigret-becomes-a-Chanel-ambassador,711142.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>法国名模 Caroline de Maigret 成为 Chanel 品牌大使</b></a>｜41 岁的法国模特、作家、音乐制作人 Caroline de Maigret 成为 Chanel 全球大使，自 1999 年起她就开始担任 Chanel 时装秀模特，今年 3 月还开始为兰蔻代言。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/7/7/12116192/maria-grazia-chiuri-leaves-valentino\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Maria Grazia Chiuri 正式卸任</b></a>｜6 月底我们曾<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/28664.html\">报道过 Dior 新创意总监可能来自 Valentino </a>的消息。周四，Valentino 在发布秋冬高级定制时装秀后，正式宣布联合创意总监 Maria Grazia Chiuri 将离职，结束八年的任期。搭档 Pierpaolo Piccioli 将继续在 Valentino 担任创意总监一职。</p><p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Avon-releases-accessories-collection-with-Tabitha-Webb,711520.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>雅芳推出配饰系列</b></a>｜美妆品牌雅芳近日与英国设计师 Tabitha Webb  合作，推出配饰系列 T by Tabitha Webb ，7 月发布，包括奢侈手袋、旅行包和钱包，印花丝巾、雨伞。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/gap-sales-june-10483711/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Gap 6月销售额增长</b></a>｜Gap 集团宣布在截至 7 月 2 日的五周内销售额有 2% 的增长，从去年同期的 15.4 亿美元增至 15.7 亿美元，可比销售额也有 2% 的增长，超出汤森路透的 3.2% 跌幅预期。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/beauty-features/revlon-taps-pamela-gill-alabaster-10483800/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>露华浓新任企业传播副总裁</b></a>｜露华浓近日宣布，Pamela Gill Alabaster 将出任企业传播及企业社会责任（CSR）部门高级副总裁，即日生效。此前他刚升任雅诗兰黛集团 CSR 部门副主席，还曾在欧莱雅美国地区工作 20 年。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>加拿大演员、导演、编剧&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/xavier-dolan-louis-vuitton-fall-winter-2016\" rel=\"nofollow\">Xavier Dolan 为 Louis Vuitton 拍摄了秋冬男装大片</a>：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708092642ap8TZbXRmrkhdFsQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666334\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708092642iAXrPxnBTzfuNt2R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708092641XZUYPOjD4JgVcoSA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667003\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>丹麦休闲户外品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/rains-2016-fw-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">RAINS 推出秋冬款 lookbook</a>：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708092753zjn0YVFI78pSK3fC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708092800euziTByxmIKbGCsH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708092758p2fzsQnx9vcHmdLY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607080927573uITkcjq6XnhoALV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607080928026Khl9CaP4ywN8cOe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708092759RzWlm6StdGan5pBY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708092803Ry8bdPmFjusYXEC0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">继 6 月宣布 Christophe Lemaire 出任“Uniqlo U”系列及优衣库巴黎研发中心艺术总监后，近日优衣库又于巴黎高定时装周期间发布&nbsp;“Uniqlo U” 首秀：<br></p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708094855CdZr8IcKD97qJtvi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.759568\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708094855Gt0CpSv13Pw9HRoe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.759568\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708094855OpyBt1dHCvze7ZxN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.608804\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607080948562ueYtOPS8wokIbT0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.613551\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708101258PwynFX23BN0LtDAv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>以杂志出名的 <i>Kinfolk</i>，旗下<a href=\"http://hypebae.com/2016/7/kinfolk-borrowed-from-the-boys?utm_source=InternalHBtoHBae&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=InternalHBtoHBaelinks\" rel=\"nofollow\">同名男装品牌发布了一组 lookbook</a>，名为“Borrowed from The Boys”，找来女模穿着拍摄，意为中性款式、男女皆可：</p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708100303Wprl6QEOnb30Twax.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708100303ythmpTYVg5oUfxZJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607081003042hwzQOcRZmFUiS68.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708100305vG8wQb2L17ZOMKms.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p class=\"\">&nbsp;OFF-WHITE 在东京新开一家旗舰店：<br></p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708102221QBNbuwLHo8OXhs9d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708102224UF2a7PXop4kDfncL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708102227c59stiYfQBVSpPqz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708102227oAmKkI8Zi1G4aFEl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708102227bujmeOA53tK0zRZ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p><br></p>"}